profile:
HOME ENERGY CONSULTING is owned and operated by Mike Gillam, a registered Energy Advisor with Natural Resources Canada. Our main focus of service is performing Home Energy Evaluations and working with homeowners and builders discover opportunities to increase energy efficiency.

As a registered Energy Advisor, Mike has a great understanding of the House-As-a-System techniques, energy conservation, and green friendly building design and technologies. Mike is also experienced in renewable energy systems and has the fundamental knowledge to design and manage project installations.

In addition, Mike is a great problem solver. He is trained to help educate homeowners on how to save energy and diagnose energy associated problems within the home and recommend what steps are required to resolve any issue(s).

Mike has been under license from his service organization Eco Advantage Energy Advisors Inc. since June 2011. During this time, he has performed over 2000+ Home Energy Evaluations. He can assist with the rating and labeling of homes under the EnerGuide Rating System. In addition, he is also an Energy Star partner and can also assist in Energy Star certification for New Homes.
 
In general, Mike is always willing to offer his assistance and would be a great asset to anyone interested in saving or generating energy. He is very devoted to his work, has excellent written and verbal communication skills, and is extremely knowledgeable in home energy consulting. When working with Mike, you can ensure all projects are completed within a professional timely manner, and to the best of his ability.
name: Home Energy Consulting
